OL,3,CMan charged with murder after fatal
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a 21 year-old was fatally
OL,8,Fstabbed in Primrose Hill, police said.
OL,10,FFinbar Sullivan died on Tuesday after
OL,11,Fthe alleged attack at the view point.
OL,13,FOn Sunday, Oliuwadamilola
OL,14,FOgunyankinnu, was charged with murder.
OL,16,FThe Metropolitan Police say the 27
OL,17,Fyear old, who is from Enfield, will
OL,18,Fappear at Stratford Magistrates' Court
OL,19,Fon Monday.
